«To Baby Angelina
Our Beautiful angel, Our hearts are filled with sorrow for having left us so soon
We love you; Miss you every moment of everyday
Mum. Dad. Sister & Family"Ė
ĄAdele (Estelle) Kruger 1941-2008
In loving memory of our mother, grandmother and best friend
We shall never forget the endless love you gave us
And your total devotion to animals"║
ĘIn Loving Memory of
Basil Kenneth Drake
15th March 1931 to 9th April 1998
Who brought his funfairs to the borough for over 40 years
and helped to raise money for various charities"Š
╗in Loving Memory of the "Three Bearham Sisters"
Ellen: 09.11.1913  02.05.2013
Rose: 18.01.1920  30.11.2012
Lillian: 13.04.1918  08.01.2000
Who Spent Many Happy Hours in Battersea Park"┐
╝Tom and Iris Gill
21 Aug 1933-18 Jan 2019 19 June 1933-10 Dec 1992
Beloved Mum, Dad, Grandad. Sharing walks & smiles together.
Enjoying music, theatre, family & a pint (or two!) for Tom"┐
