25th October 1979 - 30th August 2013
Beloved wife, daughter, sister and friend
Forever loved, always missed, never forgotten
We all miss you so much
Jamie, Thomas and Spanky"┴
ŠFor Gwyneth and Arnold, remembered with love
by their children and grandchildren
"Nature's economy shall be the base for our own,
for it is immutable, but ours is secondary" Linnaeus 1740"╦
╚Svetlana Grigorlan
13.08.1950 - 13.03.2019
If roses grew in Heaven, Lord please pick a bunch for me, place them in my
Mother's arms and tell her they're from me. Tell her I love her and miss her,
and when she turns smile, place a kiss upon her cheek and hold her for a while.
In loving memory of mum and wife that meant so much."╬
╦A Battersea girl with a heart of gold. cared for her parents growing old
She would always give her time to share, with anyone feeling in despair
When troubles seem to fill their day, helped to clear their problems away
The world is now a sadder place, without her kind and smiling face
In memory of Mabel Gladys Coote 1922-2017"Ž
╠Peter & Muriel Kenny
We wrote your name In the sand, but the waves washed it away
We wrote your name in the sky, but the clouds blew it away
So we wrote your name in our hearts and forever it will stay"į
čIn loving memory of a very special person
Gioacchino Visaggi who fell asleep on the 30 May 2016
He will be truly missed by his wife and two daughters
whom he dedicated his entire life, and all those who were
helped by his enormous generosity
He has shown to us all to never give up fighting in our
beliefs despite all the hardships"ž
šIn celebration of the marriage of
Dan Moss and Claudie Sellers
18th July 2015
So, she leaning on her husband's arm, they turned homeward
by a rosy path which the gracious sun struck out for them in its setting"█
